full_threads.body:
Hi Team,

The SGUA Pay Bill page has an issue where at certain time in a day it starts having issues with processing to the next page.
For some reason, it is unable to get to the next page. I am unable to get any error message except from the console.

My solution to this problem is to manually clear the cache on WordPress and this issue goes away every time. Is there something about the cache setting of this page/site that may be causing an issue.
I spoke to the developer, and he is of the opinion there is an issue with the caching process. Are there any suggestions for this issue?

Thanks.



Kind regards,

Sree Nair
